thread.title: BRIEF-Clicks Group Says Bookbuild Completed

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Clicks Group Says Bookbuild Completed

organizations.name: brief-clicks group says bookbuild completed feb 16

text:
Feb 16 (Reuters) - Clicks Group Ltd:
* BOOKBUILD HAS BEEN SUCCESSFULLY COMPLETED * 7 642 904 BOOKBUILD SHARES HAVE BEEN PLACED WITH 35 PARTICIPATING INVESTORS ON BEHALF OF BENEFICIARIES OF ESOP TRUST
* ‍INVESTORS TO SELL THEIR CLICKS GROUP ORDINARY SHARES AT BOOKBUILD PRICE OF R166.00 PER SHARE​
* CLICKS GROUP- PRICE REPRESENTS A DISCOUNT OF 3.7%, 0.9% AND 2.0% TO CLOSING PRICE, 3 DAY VWAP AND 30 DAY VWAP ON 15 FEBRUARY 2018 OF A CLICKS SHARE Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
